These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-5-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: thriller, family
1. the person watching family movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching thriller movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2   |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | family |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-5-2::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: grey, yellow
1. the person who likes grey is somewhere to the left of the person who likes yellow##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |  2  |
| Color   | grey | yellow |

 #################################

 
